room_title: Escape room "Murder Manor" by Escape Waukesha in Milwaukee
room_description: Cromwell has called you all to Montgomery Manor to solve the murder of Lord Robert Montgomery who was killed an hour before the reading of his revised Will. The cops have done all they can, leaving you 60 minutes to find the murderer before they have to release the guests. Could it be the vengeful ex-wife trying to stop the changing of the Will? His new, MUCH younger, wife looking to cash in before the marriage starts? The business partner who was going to be sold out by Lord Robert? Or the Butler…cause isn’t it always the Butler? Do you have what it takes to solve the case and reveal the murderer?
